snippet.title: The Upcoming
snippet.description:
The Upcoming brings you the best interviews, clips and trailers from the Cinema, Food and Music worlds.

Subscribe to our channel to get the most out of our beautiful and insightful content.

The Upcoming is based in London but we like to travel.

Want more?

Website https://www.theupcoming.co.uk
Instagram @theupcoming / @theupcomingfood
Twitter @the_upcoming
Facebook @TheUpcomingMagazine
